thread.title: Commercial National Financial Corporation Announces Quarterly Dividend

author: cnbc.com
title: Commercial National Financial Corporation Announces Quarterly Dividend
text:
ITHACA, Mich., Feb. 22, 2018 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Commercial National Financial Corporation (Pink Sheets:CEFC) announced that the Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of 13 cents per share payable April 2, 2018 to shareholders of record on March 16, 2018. Based on a recent closing price of $12.00 per share, the annualized dividend yield is 4.33%.
